PN,38301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779563472
OL,3,CGP forged prescriptions for Ozempic
OL,4,Cand other drugs for himself and family
OL,6,FA former Jersey GP has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto 210 hours of community service
OL,8,Fafter he forged the prescriptions of
OL,9,Fthree patients, over the course of
OL,10,Ffive years.
OL,12,FJersey's Royal Court heard Henryk
OL,13,FJerszy Juchniewicz who was working as
OL,14,Fa GP at Cleveland Medical Practice at
OL,15,Fthe time, prescribed multiple drugs
OL,16,Ffor himself, as well as a script for
OL,17,Fthe weight-loss drug, Ozempic, for his
OL,18,Fthen wife in the UK.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
