OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779563472
OL,3,CGP forged prescriptions for Ozempic
OL,4,Cand other drugs for himself and family
OL,6,FOver five years from March 22nd 2020
OL,7,Fto March 21st 2025 Juchniewicz forged
OL,8,F37 prescription using records of two
OL,9,Fformer patients and one current
OL,10,Fpatient.
OL,12,FIn court today, the prosecution
OL,13,Foutlined how he followed the same
OL,14,Fprocess for each of his patients -
OL,15,Fprescribing drugs, accessing them
OL,16,Fbefore cancelling the prescription to
OL,17,Favoid being detected.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779563472
OL,3,CGP forged prescriptions for Ozempic
OL,4,Cand other drugs for himself and family
OL,6,FMost of the drugs were for his own
OL,7,Fpersonal use including Modifinil - a
OL,8,Fsubstance that keeps you stay awake
OL,9,Fand prevent sleepiness. Juchniewicz's
OL,10,Fdefence advocate argued this was done
OL,11,Fto keep on top of his work which was
OL,12,Fstressful and time consuming.
OL,14,FHowever, on several occasions, he also
OL,15,Fprescribed drugs for his then ex wife
OL,16,Fwho was living in the UK. This
OL,17,Fincluded the weight-loss drug Ozempic.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779563472
OL,3,CGP forged prescriptions for Ozempic
OL,4,Cand other drugs for himself and family
OL,6,FThe former GP also prescribed a drug
OL,7,Fto his ex-partner in March 2020 which
OL,8,Fhe thought could be effective against
OL,9,FCOVID-19 after he saw it was being
OL,10,Fused in Japan at the time to combat
OL,11,Fthe virus.
OL,13,FThe court accepted the drugs were for
OL,14,Fhis personal use or for close
OL,15,Frelations and there was no financial
OL,16,Fbenefit.
OL,18,FThe forgeries came to light in June
OL,19,F2025 when concerns were raised by an
OL,20,Fex-patient, he was then arrested and
OL,21,Finterviewed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779563472
OL,3,CGP forged prescriptions for Ozempic
OL,4,Cand other drugs for himself and family
OL,6,FIn mitigation the court heard
OL,7,FJuchniewicz was under stress and in a
OL,8,Fbad relationship and self`prescribed
OL,9,Fto deal with high workload and a poor
OL,10,Fmental state.
OL,12,FDeputy Bailiff Mark Temple KC praised
OL,13,Fthe practice manager of Cleveland
OL,14,FClinic for their swift action.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779563472
OL,3,CGP forged prescriptions for Ozempic
OL,4,Cand other drugs for himself and family
OL,6,FHe told Juchniewicz: "There is no
OL,7,Fdoubt that the trust placed in the you
OL,8,Fwas absolute. You breached the trust
OL,9,Fof your patients, you breached the
OL,10,Ftrust of your surgery and you breached
OL,11,Fthe public's trust in the medical
OL,12,Fprofession."
OL,14,FTh court heard Juchniewicz was very
OL,15,Flikely to be struck off by the General
OL,16,FMedical Council.
OL,18,FHe was sentenced to 210 hours of
OL,19,Fcommunity service and to pay #1,000.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779563472
OL,3,CGP forged prescriptions for Ozempic
OL,4,Cand other drugs for himself and family
OL,6,FAfter pleading guilty, he lost his job
OL,7,Fat Cleveland Medical Practice.
OL,9,FThe manager Nell Montague-Rendall said
OL,10,Fin statement today: "As soon as we
OL,11,Fbecame aware of this incident we took
OL,12,Fimmediate steps to investigate the
OL,13,Fissue.
OL,15,F"Dr Juchniewicz has not been working
OL,16,Fin the practice since. We understand
OL,17,Fthat the matter has been dealt with by
OL,18,Fthe relevant authorities."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
